      <profileDesc>
         <abstract>
            <ab>The text of the Life of St Takla Haymanot, unspecified recension. 
               Several recensions exist, including <title ref="LIT3969GadlaTHW">Wāldǝbbā recension</title> (the earliest and shortest), <title ref="LIT3970GadlaTHH">Ḥayq recension</title>, 
            and the most widely spread <title ref="LIT1507GadlaT">Dabra Libānos recension</title>, 
               which in its turn exists in at least two sub-recensions, <title ref="LIT4114GadlaT">first Dabra Libānos sub-recension</title> and <title ref="LIT4115GadlaT">second Dabra Libānos sub-recension</title>.
               There is also a <title ref="LIT5883GadlaTHM">mixed type recension</title>.</ab>
         </abstract>
